%% Client onboarding, connect, and billing usage flow
sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User (Client)
  participant CP as Control Plane
  participant BILL as Stripe
  participant NODE as VPN Node
  participant DB as Postgres

  U->>CP: Sign up + choose plan
  CP->>BILL: create subscription
  BILL-->>CP: subscription active
  CP->>DB: create user record
  CP->>CP: generate credentials (keys)
  CP-->>U: deliver config (QR / download)
  U->>NODE: connect using config
  NODE-->>CP: session start + periodic usage reports
  CP->>DB: record session & usage
  CP->>BILL: (optional) metered billing report
  U->>CP: disconnect
  NODE-->>CP: session end
  CP->>DB: finalize usage
